  • public class MendelianCheckerXD
extends AbstractMendelianChecker
    Implementation of Mendelian compatibility check for autosomal dominant case

    Compatibility Check

    For X-chromosomal dominant inheritance, there must be at least one Genotype that is shared by all affected individuals but no unaffected individuals in the pedigree.
    Author:
    Max Schubach, Manuel Holtgrewe
